overview.en: TCASH Token is an income-generating cryptocurrency. Holders can share 50% transaction fees of EtherFlyer. EtherFlyer is a one-stop, high-volume and open source decentralized exchange.
overview.zh: TCASH代币是一种创收型的数字货币，持有者能够一起分享EtherFlyer平台上加密货币交易费用的50%。EtherFlyer是一站式，高流通性，开源的去中心化数字货币交易所。
